CMS Project procedures in detail:
1. split index.php file into several parts: 
  db.php--database connection to mysql server
  footer.php--footer file of index.php
  header.php--header file of index.php
  navigation.php--categories of navigation bar
  sidebar.php--search form and sidebar categories
  widget.ph--side widget well
  
2. Navigation.php
  A. create database called "CMS" in MySQL server
  B. create table called "categorires" under database
